  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbstractQueryFilter
    Interface for creating SOLR Query filters
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndQueryFilter
    Basic and filter with AND relation to other query filters, the values themselves have OR relation with one another.
    AndSubQueryFilter
    Class for creating AND sub queries.
    OrQueryFilter
    Basic and filter with OR relation to other query filters, the values themselves have OR relation with one another.
    OrSubQueryFilter
    class for creation OR sub queries.
    RangeQueryFilter
    Filter that supports range operations (field:[* TO *]) for Solr queries
